Masu ra'ayin siyasa a duk faɗin duniya suna jin tsoron cewa wannan zai iya zama wani abu mai tsanani.
A wani jawabin da ya yi a jam'iyyar Labour, ya ce kungiyarsa ta damu saboda taken taken taken ya yi daidai da kalmomin nan "Twp and Pwp".
