Sainsbury's na shirin kaiwa kasuwar kyau ta Birtaniya
Sainsbury's ya yi gasa da Boots, Superdrug da kuma Debenhams ta hanyar ba da kyawawan kyawawan kayayyaki a cikin shagon sayar da kayayyaki wanda ke da ƙwararrun mataimakan mata.
