Hukumar kula da yanayi ta kasa ta ce za ta ci gaba da lura da ambaliyar ruwa a yammacin Arizona da kuma kudu maso gabashin Nevada da kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, ciki har da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
