Amurka ta kara yawan kudaden da take bayarwa don bunkasa fasahar kere kere
Yayin da China ke kara daukar matakin bunkasa fasahar kere kere, ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudin da take kashewa wajen bunkasa fasahar kere kere, a cewar mai zuba jari kuma masanin fasahar kere kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google da Microsoft da kuma Apple.
Wannan ya biyo bayan sanarwar da sassan gwamnatin Amurka suka yi game da ilimin kere kere, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar kere kere a hukumance.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta sanar da shirinta a shekarar da ta gabata, inda ta ce a shekara ta 2030 ne za ta zama kasa mafi iya hada dukkan sabbin abubuwa.
"Samun kudade sau biyu na binciken ilimin kere kere zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, ganin cewa duk sauran kasashen da ke duniya ba su da yawa kamar Amurka, kuma muna neman gano sabon abu a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji Lee.
"Karuwan kudade na iya nufin karuwar damar da za a samu na tabbatar da cewa an cimma babbar nasara a fannin ilimin kere kere a Amurka", in ji Lee a wata hira da aka yi da shi a wannan makon.
Lee ya wallafa littafinsa "Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" tare da Houghton Mifflin Harcourt a wannan watan kuma shi ne Babban Daraktan Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a cikin daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin ilimin kere kere na kasar Sin, Face++.
A Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a shekarun 1980, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin fahimtar artificial wanda ya zama dan wasan Othello mafi kyau a Amurka.
Lee ya bayyana cewa ya san da previous gwamnatin Amurka fasaha gasa kamar Robotics Challenge Agency Advanced Research Projects a fannin tsaron, da kuma ya tambaye abin da lokaci zai zama na gaba domin ya taimake gane da gaba viewers.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amurka sau da yawa suna yin aiki tukuru don samun tallafi daga gwamnati.
"Shugabannin jami'o'i ba su da alhakin China, kamfanoni ne suke da alhakin", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi kokarin daukar daliban da suka yi fice a jami'a don yin aiki a kan ilimin kere kere kwanan nan.
Bugu da ƙari, Lee ya ce canje-canje a cikin manufofin ƙaura na iya taimaka wa Amurka ta ƙarfafa ƙoƙarinta a fannin ilimin kere kere.
"Na yi imanin cewa ya kamata a ba da katunan kore ta atomatik ga mutanen da ke da ƙwarewa a cikin ilimin kere kere", in ji shi.
