Wadanda ke goyon bayan sauya sunan, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev, suna jayayya cewa wannan farashi ya cancanci a biya domin Macedonia, daya daga cikin kasashe masu tasowa bayan rugujewar Yugoslavia, ta sami damar shiga kungiyoyi kamar EU da NATO.
"Na zo nan yau ne domin in kada kuri'a a kan makomar kasar nan, a kan matasan Macedonia, domin su samu damar rayuwa cikin 'yanci a karkashin inuwar Tarayyar Turai, domin hakan zai samar da rayuwa mafi aminci ga dukkanmu", in ji Georgijevska, mai shekara 79, a Skopje.
