Lokaci na Rally na Yammacin Virginia Trump, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Trump zai fara jerin gangamin kamfen dinsa a yau da dare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko cikin jerin wasannin da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, da suka haɗa da ziyara da kuma wasannin da za a yi a wurare masu kyau kamar su Tennessee da Mississippi.
A cikin wannan yanayi, Trump yana neman ya tara goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar wa'adi, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa ikon da suke da shi a majalisar dokoki lokacin da za a yi zaben a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne za a yi zaben Trump a West Virginia a daren yau, kuma ta yaya zan iya kallon shi ta yanar gizo?
Ranar Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a 7 na yammacin lokacin Gabas, ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ka iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta amfani da watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube kai tsaye.
Trump na iya tattauna batun a wannan makon na zabensa na babban alkalin kotun kolin kasar, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke fuskantar matsin lamba sakamakon zargin cin zarafin mata da aka yi masa, kuma an jinkirta zabensa a majalisar dokoki har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin jerin gangamin shi ne taimakawa 'yan ci-rani da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba su samu karfin gwiwa.
Saboda haka, kamfen din Shugaba Trump ya ce za a yi tarukan gangamin guda biyar a mako mai zuwa da nufin tayar da hankalin masu ba da tallafi da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke neman karewa da kuma kara yawan rinjayen da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Gwamnatin da ke karkashin majalisar wakilai na da matukar muhimmanci a ajandarsu har da shugaban kasa zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama yadda zai iya a lokacin da za a fara muhimmin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump, wanda bai bayyana sunansa ba, a hirar da ya yi da kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
Ana gudanar da shi a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Wheeling, za a iya samun magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun rahoto daga Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia karo na biyu a watan da ya gabata, inda ya samu fiye da kashi 40 cikin 100 a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar Majalisar Dattijai na Republican zuwa West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a cikin sandunan fensho.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo nan don ƙoƙarin tura shi a cikin sandunan fil", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
