Turai ta kai 10-6 a ranar karshe Ryder Cup
Turai na da babbar nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta yi nasara a wasan kwallon kwando da kuma wasan dab da-dabam a ranar Asabar da ci 10-6 a kan Amurka.
'Yan wasa biyu masu ban mamaki Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci yakin tare da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods don ci gaba da zira kwallaye a Le Golf National zuwa maki hudu.
A wasan farko da suka buga a wasan farko, kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai Thomas Bjorn, wadda take neman ta lashe kofin da ta yi hasara a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta yi nasara a kan kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Amurka a cikin wasannin da suka buga a cikin safiya, inda suka ci 3-1.
The UDA ya ba mafi yawan juriya a cikin hudu, amma ba za su iya cire da rashin.
Jim Furyk ya bukaci maki takwas daga cikin 12 da za a buga a ranar Lahadi don ya ci gaba da wasa.
Fleetwood ne na farko Turai rookie to lashe hudu a jere maki kuma shi da Molinari, wanda aka kira "Molliwood" bayan wani m karshen mako, ne na biyu bar to lashe hudu maki daga hudu na farko wasanni a Ryder Cup tarihi.
Bayan ya kara da Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin ƙwallon ƙafa huɗu sun yi aiki tare don doke Woods a kan Bryson American na farko da ya fara 5 da 4.
Wood, wanda ya buga wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya yi wasu dama na musamman amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 a cikin wasanni hudu da hudu da kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda aka yi wa rashin lafiya a cikin hudu na safe, ya dawo a matsayin abokin hulɗa na Henrik Stenson a cikin 'yan wasan da suka doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka na farko da na uku a duniya 2 da 1.
Dukkanin abubuwan da suka faru a Turai sun kasance masu ban tsoro da kuma ban tsoro a wata rana mai ban tsoro a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth, wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni uku, da Justin Thomas sun sa Amurkawa su yi nasara da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain da kwallaye 2 da 1 a kwallaye huɗu kuma daga baya suka doke Polter da Rory McIlroy da kwallaye 4 da 3 a cikin kwallaye huɗu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup wata kungiya ta dawo daga tazarar maki hudu a farkon wasannin, yayin da Furyk ya bukaci a ci shi da maki daya domin shi ne mai rike kofin.
Amma bayan kasancewa na biyu na kwana biyu, ya zo ya yi sallama a ranar Lahadi yana kallon kamar idan ya kasance fiye da iyawa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta amince da mulkin kama karya ba ba tare da amincewa da juna ba
A ranar Asabar, ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya yi jawabi ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa, takunkumin da ake ci gaba da sanyawa Amurka na kara tsanantawa, kuma kasar ba za ta kawar da makaman nukiliyarta ba bisa son ranta.
Ri Yong Ho ya fadawa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki matakai masu kyau a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da ayyukan nukiliya da kuma harkokin sadarwa, da dakatar da wani wurin gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin da ta yi na kin yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
