Game da kursiyin taurari Kit Harington ya kashe wani mai guba da'ira
Kit Harington ya fi shahara a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na HBO mai ban mamaki Game of Thrones.
Amma dan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi watsi da ra'ayin da ake da shi na jarumin macho, yana mai cewa yin irin wannan rawar a allon ya sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su kasance masu taurin kai don a girmama su.
Da yake magana da Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce yana ganin akwai wani abu da ya faru kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar maza masu guba a cikin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda ya auri 'yar wasan kwaikwayo ta Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, kuma mai shekara 31, a kwanan nan, ya yarda cewa yana jin ƙarfin gwiwa don magance matsalar.
"Na ji ƙarfi a cikin minti daya - abin da ya tafi a can tare da wahayi?" ya ce.
Me muka koya wa maza yayin da suke girma, game da matsalar da muke da ita yanzu?
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na da alhakin karuwar masu fama da cutar saboda halayen da ke nuna irin wannan cutar.
"Sai ta ce, 'Wace ce wannan mai hikima, ko kuwa wanda aka koya masa?'
Menene ake koya a talabijin, da kuma a kan tituna, da ke sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su zama wani irin mutum na musamman?
Ina ganin wannan ita ce babbar tambayar da muke fuskanta - ta yaya za mu canja wannan?
Domin a bayyane yake cewa wani abu ya tafi daga nan zuwa matasa maza.
