A kwanan baya, ya ce ganawa da matarsa Rose shi ne abu mafi kyau da ya ji a Game of Thrones.
"Na sadu da wata mata a shirin, don haka a wata hanya ta ba ni iyalina, da kuma rayuwata daga nan", in ji shi.
Rose ta taka rawa a matsayin Ygritte, ƙaunataccen Jon Snow na Kit, a cikin shirin mai ban mamaki da ya lashe Emmy.
