Makonni bayan da daya daga cikin jaridun kasar Sin na hukuma ya wallafa wani shafi na hudu a cikin wata jarida ta Amurka da ke inganta cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da kafofin watsa labarai na Amurka don yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba, Shugaba Donald Trump ya yi tsokaci game da harin da aka kai wa China Daily a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi ko ina samun bugawa a Iowa, bayan da aka zargi China da yin katsalandanci a zaben shugaban kasa da aka gudanar a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka wani sabon mataki ne na kokarin Washington na matsawa China lamba.
Duk da cewa ya zama al'ada ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya sanarwar da ke inganta kasuwanci, a halin yanzu Beijing da Washington suna fama da yakin cinikayya wanda ya haifar da kasashen biyu da ke sanya harajin shigo da juna.
A cikin yakin cinikayya, China ta yi amfani da haraji don kai hari ga masu fitar da kayayyaki daga wasu jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana daga Amurka da China.
Terry Branstad, Jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin noma zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wani yanki a cikin Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, "China yanzu tabbatar da cewa cin zarafi da gudu propaganda talla a mu free jarida".
"A wajen yada farfagandar ta, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da muhimmiyar al'adar Amurka ta 'yancin fadin albarkacin baki da' yancin 'yan jarida ta hanyar sanya talla da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a cikin kantin jaridu da ke kan titi a nan Beijing, za ku sami wahalar samun maganganu da ba za su iya ba da hujja ba kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayoyi daban-daban da mutanen Sin suke da shi game da al'amuran tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda jaridar da ke ƙarƙashin jagorancin Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin", in ji shi.
