A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin kare hakkin 'yan majalisa na Jamus ya yarda cewa jirgin ruwan na Jamus yana gudu ne daga jiragen ruwa da za a iya gano su.
