Taron Trump da Rosenstein na iya sake jinkirta, in ji fadar White House
Babban taron Donald Trump da babban sakataren kasa Rod Rosenstein na iya jinkirta zuwa mako guda yayin da ake ci gaba da fafatawa a kan Brett Kavanaugh, a cewar fadar White House a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein ya jagoranci aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken tsoma baki na Rasha a cikin zaben, hulɗa tsakanin masu ba da shawara na Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar hanawa shugaban adalci.
Ko Trump zai janye takardar neman a sake zaben shugaban kasa, wanda hakan zai yi wa Mueller barazana, ya kasance batun da Washington ke ta kokarin warwarewa na tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, New York Times ta ba da rahoton cewa Rosenstein ya yi la'akari da sanya na'urar don yin rikodin tattaunawar da Trump tare da yiwuwar kawar da shugaban ta amfani da 25th gyare-gyare.
Rosenstein ya kira wannan rahoto.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya je Fadar White House, saboda an ce yana shirin yin murabus.
Amma a maimakon haka, an sanar da taron da za a yi ranar Alhamis da Trump, wanda a lokacin yana Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce zai fi dacewa ya dakatar da Rosenstein amma sai aka dage taron don kauce wa rikici da sauraron kotun majalisa, inda Kavanaugh da daya daga cikin matan da aka tuhuma da cin zarafin mata, Dr Christine Blasey Ford, suka bayar da shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya umarci FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh, inda ya dage kuri'ar da aka kada a majalisar dattijai.
