Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka addabi birnin Palu a kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Tare da katsewar sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su sami damar samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palau wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5.
A Palau, mutane fiye da 16,000 sun tsere bayan girgizar kasa ta afka musu.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birni ne na lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, a ƙarshen ƙauyen bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a na 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin ranar haihuwarsa na 40 a lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai tsawo na sama da kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, yanki ne na gwamnati a ƙarƙashin lardin, yana da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a na 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan masu ba da gudummawa ga tattalin arzikin jihar Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
Har ila yau, akwai ma'adinan hakar ma'adinai a cikin lardin, amma mafi yawan wannan aikin yana faruwa a Morowali, a gabar tsibirin.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, wata guguwar ruwa da ake kira tsunami ta halaka mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afka yammacin Donggala a 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana zaune a kan Pacific Tsari na Tsaro na Tsaro kuma ana fama da girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wata girgizar kasa da ta auku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ta addabi kasashe 14, inda ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ya afkawa gabar tekun yammacin Sumatra a karshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
An kashe ɗarurruwan mutane a tsibirin Nias da ke kusa da Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai girman 6.8 ta afkawa Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ta afka wa gabar kudu maso gabar teku, inda ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai girman mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta girgiza tashar jirgin ruwa ta Pidie Jaya a Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da firgici yayin da aka tunatar da mutane game da bala'in girgizar kasa da bala'in tsunami na 2004 da kuma bala'in tsunami.
A wannan karon ba tsunami ba ne ya haddasa guguwar, amma faɗuwar gine-gine ya kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Manyan girgizar kasa sun afkawa Lombok, tsibirin da ke Indonesia, inda suka kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido sun makale a wurin.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin kan zargin cin zarafin mata
